cat << EOF
scanlogd is a TCP port scan detection tool, originally designed to 
illustrate various attacks an IDS developer has to deal with, for a
Phrack Magazine article. Thus, unlike some of the other port scan 
detection tools out there, scanlogd is designed to be totally safe 
to use.
EOF
